   "about_us": "About Us",
  "paragraph_1": "Welcome to Pizza Pete’s, where passion for authentic Italian flavors meets the joy of sharing food with loved ones. Our journey began with a simple goal: to bring the freshest ingredients and carefully crafted recipes to every table. From hand-stretched dough to perfectly melted cheese, every pizza we serve is a testament to our dedication to quality and flavor.",
  "paragraph_2": "At Pizza Pete’s, we believe that a meal is more than just food – it's an experience. Our cozy ambiance, friendly staff, and commitment to excellent service make each visit memorable. We take pride in sourcing the finest locally-grown vegetables, premium meats, and the freshest herbs to guarantee a delightful taste in every bite.",
  "paragraph_3": "Whether you are joining us for a family dinner, celebrating a special occasion, or just craving a delicious pizza, Pizza Pete’s is here to make every moment enjoyable. Our menu also features a variety of sides, desserts, and beverages, designed to complement your meal perfectly. Thank you for choosing Pizza Pete’s – where quality, passion, and happiness come together in every slice!",
